{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/terms-and-conditions/layout,_N_T_/terms-and-conditions/page,_N_T_/terms-and-conditions"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/terms-and-conditions/__PAGE__","/terms-and-conditions","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\" class=\"geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable geist_mono_8d43a2aa-module__8Li5zG__variable\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.09zddjkbdep5a.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.09~u27dqhyhd6.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0wltabvkfu~52.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0yb2wil16uz6h.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0txnolcfq7_.a.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/10u3y4bw1ayzs.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/07f1qd~q5490h.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0pqt~8bl3ukh4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-0bhhnp1_t825g.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j_2f.5rtsp.w.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/07zvm8guukd7o.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/05dskxuewo-er.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/07-oa-9k360xq.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/019fwsi-i0n2g.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/12i2rjs~x5x.h.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0_g3r3w8abg4c.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"/><title>My Store Grocery — Fresh Groceries Delivered Fast</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Order farm-fresh organic produce, daily essentials &amp; household items online. Fast delivery to your doorstep within 24 hours. Serving Satara &amp; nearby areas.\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"grocery,delivery,fresh produce,organic,online grocery,My Store,farm fresh,Satara,India\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"My Store Grocery — Fresh Groceries Delivered Fast\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Order farm-fresh organic produce, daily essentials &amp; household items online. Fast delivery to your doorstep within 24 hours.\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"My Store Grocery\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"My Store Grocery — Fresh Groceries Delivered Fast\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Order farm-fresh organic produce, daily essentials &amp; household items online. Fast delivery to your doorstep within 24 hours.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"font-sans antialiased bg-gray-50\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script>((a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h)=>{let i=document.documentElement,j=[\"light\",\"dark\"];function k(b){var c;(Array.isArray(a)?a:[a]).forEach(a=>{let c=\"class\"===a,d=c&&f?e.map(a=>f[a]||a):e;c?(i.classList.remove(...d),i.classList.add(f&&f[b]?f[b]:b)):i.setAttribute(a,b)}),c=b,h&&j.includes(c)&&(i.style.colorScheme=c)}if(d)k(d);else try{let a=localStorage.getItem(b)||c,d=g&&\"system\"===a?window.matchMedia(\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\").matches?\"dark\":\"light\":a;k(d)}catch(a){}})(\"class\",\"theme\",\"light\",null,[\"light\",\"dark\"],null,true,true)</script><nav class=\"w-full bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-zinc-100 fixed top-0 left-0 z-50 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"hidden sm:block bg-emerald-600 text-white text-xs font-semibold py-1.5 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><a href=\"tel:+919876543210\" class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-emerald-100 transition\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-phone w-3 h-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13.832 16.568a1 1 0 0 0 1.213-.303l.355-.465A2 2 0 0 1 17 15h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2A18 18 0 0 1 2 4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-.8 1.6l-.468.351a1 1 0 0 0-.292 1.233 14 14 0 0 0 6.392 6.384\"></path></svg><span>+91 98765 43210</span></a><a href=\"mailto:support@mystoregrocery.in\" class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-emerald-100 transition\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail w-3 h-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg><span>support@mystoregrocery.in</span></a></div><span class=\"text-[10px] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-100\">Fresh Grocery Express</span></div></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center h-16\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 shrink-0\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-md\"><span class=\"text-white text-sm font-black\">M</span></div><span class=\"text-lg font-black bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-700 to-teal-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent hidden sm:block\">My Store Grocery</span></a><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors text-zinc-600 hover:text-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-50\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors text-zinc-600 hover:text-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-50\" href=\"/products\">Products</a><a class=\"px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors text-zinc-600 hover:text-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-50\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold transition-colors text-zinc-600 hover:text-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-50\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3\"><button class=\"relative flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 px-3 py-2 rounded-xl hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-colors border border-emerald-100\" aria-label=\"Open shopping cart\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shopping-cart w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"21\" r=\"1\"></circle><circle cx=\"19\" cy=\"21\" r=\"1\"></circle><path d=\"M2.05 2.05h2l2.66 12.42a2 2 0 0 0 2 1.58h9.78a2 2 0 0 0 1.95-1.57l1.65-7.43H5.12\"></path></svg><div class=\"hidden sm:flex flex-col items-end\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-semibold text-emerald-600 leading-tight\">Cart</span><span class=\"text-sm font-bold leading-tight\">₹<!-- -->0</span></div></button><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-teal-600 hover:from-emerald-700 hover:to-teal-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\" href=\"/auth\">Sign In</a><button class=\"md:hidden p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu w-5 h-5 text-zinc-700\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></nav><main class=\"pt-16 md:pt-16 min-h-screen\"><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 via-white to-teal-50\"><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-700 via-teal-700 to-emerald-800 text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-6\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-white/15 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text w-10 h-10 text-emerald-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-emerald-200 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase\">Legal</p><h1 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight\">📜 Terms &amp; Conditions</h1></div></div><p class=\"text-emerald-100 text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed\">By using our platform, you agree to these terms. Please read them carefully to understand your rights and obligations when using the<!-- -->My Store Grocery<!-- --> platform.</p></div></div><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"space-y-8\"><section class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg shrink-0\">1</span><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg>Introduction &amp; Acceptance of Terms</h2></div></div><div class=\"ml-14 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>1. Acceptance of Terms By accessing or using the platform, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree with any part of these Terms, you must not use our services.</p><p>These Terms constitute a legally binding agreement between you (&quot;User&quot;) and <!-- -->My Store Grocery<!-- -->(&quot;Company&quot;, &quot;we&quot;, &quot;our&quot;, or &quot;us&quot;) regarding your use of the platform.</p><p>The Company reserves the right to update or modify these Terms at any time without prior notice. Your continued use of the platform following any changes constitutes your acceptance of the new Terms.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg shrink-0\">2</span><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg>Account Registration &amp; Eligibility</h2></div></div><div class=\"ml-14 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>To use certain features of our platform, you must create an account and meet the following eligibility criteria:</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>You must be at least <strong>18 years of age</strong> or have the consent of a parent/guardian to use our services.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>You must provide <strong>accurate, current, and complete</strong> <!-- -->information during registration and keep it updated.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>You are solely responsible for maintaining the<!-- --> <strong>confidentiality of your login credentials</strong> and for all activities under your account.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>You must <strong>immediately notify us</strong> of any unauthorised access to your account at support@mystoregrocery.in.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>We reserve the right to<!-- --> <strong>suspend or terminate accounts</strong> that violate these Terms or engage in fraudulent activity.</span></li></ul></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg shrink-0\">3</span><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shopping-cart w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"21\" r=\"1\"></circle><circle cx=\"19\" cy=\"21\" r=\"1\"></circle><path d=\"M2.05 2.05h2l2.66 12.42a2 2 0 0 0 2 1.58h9.78a2 2 0 0 0 1.95-1.57l1.65-7.43H5.12\"></path></svg>Orders &amp; Product Availability</h2></div></div><div class=\"ml-14 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>When you place an order through our platform, you make an offer to purchase the selected products subject to the following conditions:</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>All orders are subject to<!-- --> <strong>availability and acceptance</strong> by us. We reserve the right to refuse or cancel any order at our discretion.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>Product images are <strong>indicative</strong> and actual products may vary slightly in appearance, packaging, or weight. For fresh produce and perishable items, natural variations are expected.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>We strive to maintain accurate stock information; however, in cases of <strong>stock-out</strong>, we may substitute with a product of equal or higher value with your consent, or issue a refund for the unavailable item.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>An order confirmation email/SMS does not constitute acceptance. The contract is formed only when the<!-- --> <strong>order is dispatched</strong>.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span><strong>Minimum order value</strong> and<!-- --> <strong>maximum order quantity</strong> restrictions may apply as specified on the platform.</span></li></ul></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg shrink-0\">4</span><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-indian-rupee w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 3h12\"></path><path d=\"M6 8h12\"></path><path d=\"m6 13 8.5 8\"></path><path d=\"M6 13h3\"></path><path d=\"M9 13c6.667 0 6.667-10 0-10\"></path></svg>Pricing &amp; Payment</h2></div></div><div class=\"ml-14 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>All prices displayed on our platform are in Indian Rupees (₹) and are inclusive of applicable GST unless otherwise stated:</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>Prices are subject to change without prior notice. The price applicable is the one displayed at the<!-- --> <strong>time of placing your order</strong>.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>In case of <strong>pricing errors</strong> (e.g., due to technical glitches), we reserve the right to cancel the order and issue a full refund.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>We accept payments via<!-- --> <strong>UPI, credit/debit cards, net banking, wallets, and Cash on Delivery (COD)</strong> <!-- -->where available. All online payments are processed through RBI-authorised payment gateways.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span><strong>GST invoices</strong> will be issued for all orders as per applicable tax regulations. GSTIN: 27AABCM1234A1Z5.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>Promotional discounts, coupons, and offers are subject to specific terms, may have<!-- --> <strong>usage limits and expiry dates</strong>, and cannot be combined unless explicitly stated.</span></li></ul></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg shrink-0\">5</span><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-truck w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14 18V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v11a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h2\"></path><path d=\"M15 18H9\"></path><path d=\"M19 18h2a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-3.65a1 1 0 0 0-.22-.624l-3.48-4.35A1 1 0 0 0 17.52 8H14\"></path><circle cx=\"17\" cy=\"18\" r=\"2\"></circle><circle cx=\"7\" cy=\"18\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg>Delivery Terms</h2></div></div><div class=\"ml-14 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>We endeavour to deliver your orders within the estimated time frame; however, delivery times are indicative and not guaranteed:</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>Standard delivery within our service area is typically<!-- --> <strong>24 to 48 hours</strong> from order confirmation, subject to product availability and weather conditions.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span><strong>Risk of loss and title</strong> for products passes to you upon delivery at the specified delivery address.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>You must ensure that someone is available to<!-- --> <strong>receive the delivery</strong> at the specified address. Failed delivery attempts may result in additional delivery charges.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>We shall not be liable for delays caused by<!-- --> <strong>force majeure events</strong> including but not limited to natural disasters, strikes, lockdowns, or government restrictions.</span></li></ul></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg shrink-0\">6</span><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-rotate-ccw w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 0-6.74 2.74L3 8\"></path><path d=\"M3 3v5h5\"></path></svg>Returns, Refunds &amp; Cancellations</h2></div></div><div class=\"ml-14 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>Our returns and refund policy is designed to ensure customer satisfaction while maintaining fair business practices:</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>Orders may be <strong>cancelled free of charge</strong> before dispatch. Cancellation after dispatch may attract a cancellation fee.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>Returns are accepted for<!-- --> <strong>damaged, defective, or incorrect items</strong> reported within 24 hours of delivery with photographic evidence.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span><strong>Perishable items</strong> (fruits, vegetables, dairy, meat) must be inspected at the time of delivery. Claims after acceptance may not be entertained.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>Approved refunds will be processed within<!-- --> <strong>3-5 business days</strong> to the original payment method. COD refunds will be credited to your store wallet or bank account.</span></li></ul><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">For detailed information, please refer to our dedicated<!-- --> <a href=\"/refund-policy\" class=\"text-emerald-600 underline hover:text-emerald-700\">Refund Policy</a> <!-- -->page.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg shrink-0\">7</span><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg>Limitation of Liability</h2></div></div><div class=\"ml-14 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>To the maximum extent permitted by applicable Indian law:</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>Our platform and services are provided on an<!-- --> <strong>&quot;as is&quot; and &quot;as available&quot;</strong> basis without warranties of any kind, whether express or implied.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>We shall not be liable for any<!-- --> <strong>indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages</strong>, including but not limited to loss of profits, data, or goodwill.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>Our total aggregate liability for any claims arising out of or relating to these Terms or the services shall not exceed the<!-- --> <strong>total amount paid by you in the 12 months preceding the claim</strong>.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>We do not guarantee uninterrupted, secure, or error-free operation of the platform. We are not liable for losses arising from<!-- --> <strong>technical failures, internet disruptions, or third-party service outages</strong>.</span></li></ul><div class=\"bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl p-4\"><p class=\"text-red-700 text-sm\"><strong>Indemnification:</strong> You agree to indemnify and hold harmless My Store Grocery Logistics Pvt. Ltd., its directors, officers, employees, and agents from any claims, damages, or expenses arising from your breach of these Terms or misuse of our services.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 shadow-sm p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 font-bold text-lg shrink-0\">8</span><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-gavel w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m14 13-8.381 8.38a1 1 0 0 1-3.001-3l8.384-8.381\"></path><path d=\"m16 16 6-6\"></path><path d=\"m21.5 10.5-8-8\"></path><path d=\"m8 8 6-6\"></path><path d=\"m8.5 7.5 8 8\"></path></svg>Governing Law &amp; Dispute Resolution</h2></div></div><div class=\"ml-14 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>These Terms and Conditions shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India:</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>These Terms are governed by the<!-- --> <strong>Indian Contract Act, 1872; the Information Technology Act, 2000; the Consumer Protection Act, 2019</strong>; and other applicable Indian legislation.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>Any dispute arising out of or in connection with these Terms shall first be attempted to be resolved through<!-- --> <strong>amicable negotiation</strong> within 30 days.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>If negotiation fails, the dispute shall be referred to<!-- --> <strong>arbitration under the Arbitration and Conciliation Act, 1996</strong>, with a sole arbitrator appointed mutually. The seat of arbitration shall be Mumbai, Maharashtra.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>The <strong>courts of Mumbai</strong> shall have exclusive jurisdiction over any proceedings relating to these Terms.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-1 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shrink-0\"></span><span>Consumer complaints may also be filed on the<!-- --> <strong>National Consumer Helpline (NCH) at 1800-11-4000</strong> <!-- -->or through the e-Daakhil portal (<em>edaakhil.nic.in</em>).</span></li></ul></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-600 to-teal-700 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 text-white\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-5\"><div class=\"p-2 bg-white/20 rounded-xl\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"cu